PRIVACY POLICY

The company Volodymyr Husliev (hereinafter referred to as "we", "us", or "our") develops mobile applications and provides them to users free of charge, with advertising support. This Privacy Policy is intended to inform users about the methods of collection, use, and disclosure of personal information when using our applications.

Collection and Use of Information
To improve the quality of our applications, we may ask you to provide personal information. The collected information will be used in accordance with this policy.

Our applications may use third-party services that may collect information used to identify you.
Third-party Services used by our applications:

  • Google Play Services
  • AdMob
  • Google Analytics for Firebase
  • Firebase Crashlytics
  • Unity

Additional Information:
Information you provide to us:
    Payment Information: When making purchases or subscriptions, you may provide payment information, such as your name, contact details (address, email), and payment method details.
    Communication with us: You may provide information if you decide to contact us (e.g., via email or providing feedback).

Information we collect when you use our applications:
    Device Information: We collect information about your device, including mobile identifiers, device type, operating system version, and app-related information.
    Diagnostic Information: We may collect information about the requests you send to our servers.
    Usage Information: We log session data, including bandwidth usage and similar diagnostic information. We may also assign a unique hash identifier to your device for activity tracking.

How we use your information:
    To communicate with users and improve service quality.
    To analyze and optimize our applications to provide a better user experience.
    To develop new applications and improve existing ones based on user feedback.
    To carry out advertising and marketing activities without using your online activity data.

Cookies and Other Tracking Technologies:
Our applications may use cookies and other tracking technologies provided by third-party services such as Google Analytics and AdMob. You can choose to accept or reject cookies in your device settings.

International Data Transfers:
We may transfer your personal data to other countries to ensure the functioning of our applications. If you are a resident of the UK or the EEA and use our applications, you acknowledge that data transfers occur at your request and with your explicit consent.

Logs:
We collect data about your device, such as IP address, device name, operating system version, and other statistical information when the app encounters errors.

Security:
We take commercially reasonable measures to protect your personal information. However, aside from standard security practices, there is no completely secure method of data transmission over the Internet, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.

Links to Third-Party Sites:
Our applications may contain links to third-party sites. We are not responsible for the content or privacy practices of these sites. We strongly encourage you to review their privacy policy.

Childrenâ€™s Privacy:
Our applications are not intended for individuals under the age of 16, and we do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If we become aware that a child under the age of 16 has provided us with personal data, we will promptly delete that information.

Changes to this Privacy Policy:
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. You should periodically review this page for changes. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new version of the Privacy Policy on this page.

These privacy and policy are effective as of 2024-11-18.

Contact Information:
If you have any questions or suggestions regarding our Privacy Policy, please contact us at: huslievdeveloper@gmail.com
